		data-flex-grow=&#34;200&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;480px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;那么还有一个是什么呢，小范围转换为大范围（扩展负数）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://airmuamua.github.io/hugoweb/p/b004/jtc11.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1879&#34;
	height=&#34;773&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://airmuamua.github.io/hugoweb/p/b004/jtc11_hu_14041cba4070f5d7.png 480w, https://airmuamua.github.io/hugoweb/p/b004/jtc11_hu_7ddab249c57e5751.png 1024w&#34;
